        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>You siphon off a portion of the target's soul to bolster your<br />own vitality. The target must attempt a Fortitude save or take 1d4 negative damage. You gain temporary Hit Points equal to the total amount of HP the target loses, including the HP lost from becoming @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and becomes<br />@Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and<br />becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 2}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> Increase the damage by 1d4.</p>"
